  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Smart Audio Broadcasting",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti AI Horn Speaker (model: UP-AI-Horn-Speaker-W) is a high-powered, intelligent network speaker built for real-time announcements in both indoor and outdoor environments. Integrated with the UniFi Access platform, it enables seamless deployment with other UniFi devices, offering advanced audio functionality through IP-based communication. The speaker supports AI-enhanced features such as text-to-speech, live paging, and pre-recorded announcements, making it ideal for public spaces, campuses, industrial zones, and security applications. Powered via 802.3af PoE, the device eliminates the need for a separate power source and simplifies installation. SIP protocol support allows it to integrate into VoIP paging systems, while compatibility with UniFi Talk and Protect enables centralized cloud-based management. The directional horn design ensures focused sound projection, delivering up to 100 dB at 1 meter with high clarity, perfect for specific zones like building entrances, corridors, or parking areas."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Rugged and Weatherproof Design",
      "text": "Designed to withstand harsh conditions, the AI Horn Speaker features a rugged IP66-rated enclosure that protects against dust, rain, and extreme weather. Its UV-resistant housing preserves its appearance and integrity in outdoor settings. Built to operate in temperatures ranging from -30°C to 60°C, the speaker is ideal for environments such as warehouses, school grounds, factories, and transit stations. Installation is flexible thanks to an included adjustable bracket for wall or pole mounting. The speaker integrates fully with the UniFi OS Console, allowing administrators to configure audio zones, automate announcements based on camera or sensor events, and manage multiple speakers at once. It supports multilingual voice prompts, real-time streaming, and secure TLS-encrypted communication. Firmware updates can be deployed remotely via the UniFi Cloud, making the AI Horn Speaker a reliable, scalable, and intelligent choice for modern audio communication needs."
    }
  ],
